msgid "Example of an Excel application for a batch-like processing"
msgstr ""

#: ../../doc_files/batch_mode/example_Excel_batch.rst:5
msgid ""
"**Platform compatibility**: This Excel batch mode example is **Windows-"
"only**. It requires **Microsoft Excel** with VBA support. **LibreOffice "
"Calc and other spreadsheet applications are not supported**. The Excel "
"file is provided as an example to demonstrate the possibility of batch "
"processing, not as a required component for using UncertRadio."
msgstr ""

#: ../../doc_files/batch_mode/example_Excel_batch.rst:11
msgid ""
"The filenames of UR projects to be processed are collected in column A of"
" Table6 and the associated Sample_IDs in column B, respectively. In this "
"example all UR example project files belonging to the program are listed "
"there."
msgstr ""

